# Voxen — AI Speech Coaching Platform

**Tagline:** Your AI-powered speaking coach. Practice. Improve. Speak with confidence.

## What We're Building

1. **Speech Evaluator** — User speaks; three expert AI voices return audio feedback.
2. **Voice Coach** — Real-time spoken coaching via ElevenLabs Conversational AI.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework:** Next.js App Router — always `app/`, never `pages/`
- **Language:** TypeScript only (`.ts` / `.tsx`)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS only — no separate CSS files, no inline styles
- **Database:** Supabase — `import { supabase } from '@/lib/supabase'`
- **Primary LLM:** OpenAI GPT-4o — `import { openai } from '@/lib/openai'`
- **Fallback LLM:** Groq `llama-3.3-70b-versatile` — `import { groq } from '@/lib/groq'` (catch blocks only)
- **Voice:** ElevenLabs STT, TTS, and Conversational AI (voice-coach only)
- **Deploy:** Vercel

Do not add a user-facing model selector. Use GPT-4o by default; mention swappable architecture in the pitch only.

## Security (never break)

- `OPENAI_API_KEY`, `ELEVENLABS_API_KEY`, `GROQ_API_KEY` are server-side only — only in `app/api/` routes
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL` and `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` are safe client-side
- Never `console.log` keys or tokens
- Validate request body fields in every API route before use

## Folder Ownership

**Team A (speech evaluator):** `app/speech-eval/**`, `app/api/analyze/**`, `app/api/speak/**`, `app/api/generate-topic/**`

**Team B (voice coach):** `app/voice-coach/**`, `app/api/voice-coach/**`

**Shared (coordinate first):** `app/layout.tsx`, `app/page.tsx`, `app/dashboard/**`, `app/api/save-session/**`, `lib/**`

## Shared Clients — import, never reinitialize

```typescript
import { supabase } from '@/lib/supabase'
import { openai } from '@/lib/openai'
import { groq } from '@/lib/groq'
```

## Git

- Never commit directly to `dev` or `main`
- Branch: `feature/yourname-description`
- Commits: `feat: …`, `fix: …`, `style: …`
- PR to `dev` when a feature chunk works end-to-end
- `git pull origin dev` before new work

## Do Not

- Call OpenAI or ElevenLabs from client components
- Create new `lib/` files without team agreement
- Change `layout.tsx` or install packages without team agreement
- Hardcode API keys
- Skip try/catch on API calls
- Leave TODOs in submitted code
- Redesign V0-pasted UI in Cursor — integrate only
